| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1031 — Recovery Inhibition (hunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e0b4720b-ce4c-5989-82d4-9dc90e7ca68e"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
